               <h1 class="my-3">Database Management System</h1>
               <p class="my-3">A Database Management System (DBMS) is a software system that is designed to manage and
                  organize data in a structured manner. It allows users to create, modify, and query a database, as well
                  as manage the security and access controls for that database.
                  DBMS provides an environment to store and retrieve the data in coinvent and efficient manner.</p>
